Conducted a comprehensive IAM access audit and policy hardening project on AWS. The goal was to identify overly permissive IAM roles, apply the principle of least privilege, and enforce MFA across key user accounts. This initiative improved the cloud environmentâ€™s security posture and reduced the attack surface.

